Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.20,0:00:01.60,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Then, will you come over?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.60,0:00:02.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.50,0:00:04.03,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Tonight… to my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.60,0:00:06.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.65,0:00:07.94,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.77,0:00:12.44,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.74,0:00:13.88,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Please!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.51,0:00:18.51,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'll get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.85,0:00:24.09,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,H… Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.85,0:00:26.39,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.96,0:00:31.09,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,This is Fukushima~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.84,0:00:43.91,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.31,0:00:49.48,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I met you last time. At Iwaya's…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.48,0:00:51.21,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,If you're looking for Sumire-chan, she's not here right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.21,0:00:51.81,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.65,0:01:03.06,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}My name is Momo. I am the unofficial pet of a certain woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.22,0:01:05.06,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I have absolutely no human rights.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.13,0:01:09.90,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}And this, by the way, is my master's official lover.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.00,0:01:14.77,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Tokyo University graduate, with a height of 183 cm,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.77,0:01:17.41,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}and an annual minimum salary of ¥120,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:20.64,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}It has been about two months since I became her pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.91,0:01:23.81,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}With food, bath… but no sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.95,0:01:27.35,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}This lifestyle with my master has been pretty thrilling.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.68,0:01:32.72,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}But lately, she's been too busy with her sweet and handsome new boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.85,0:01:35.89,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I may be feeling jealous… as a dog would.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.89,0:01:38.96,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,What kind of a relationship are you in, if you can't even be yourself in front of your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.96,0:01:41.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not that I can't show my true self.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.17,0:01:45.37,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.43,0:01:48.14,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Honestly speaking,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.51,0:01:54.58,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm pretty excited about these circumstances now.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:56.51,0:01:57.51,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,You know, I…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.51,0:01:58.58,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.71,0:02:02.75,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hello…? Iwaya-san…?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.82,0:02:08.06,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You were the one who called just a while ago, weren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.56,0:02:13.86,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.10,0:02:20.14,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why… are you there?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.97,0:02:26.47,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Can't you see that he's letting me spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.01,0:02:32.01,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Shall I explain things in further detail?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.72,0:02:40.22,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You should've listened…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.16,0:02:42.62,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,Iwaya-san, you're here?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.32,0:02:45.53,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Apparently the server has shut down.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.53,0:02:47.76,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,I was drinking downstairs, but I came rushing up as soon as I heard.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.00,0:02:50.03,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I'm afraid to learn the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.47,0:02:55.74,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I don't have the courage to even listen to excuses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.40,0:02:59.01,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,This is Fukushima~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.01,0:03:01.11,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Can't you see that he's letting me spend the night?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.79,0:03:17.49,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.77,0:03:27.97,title,text,0,0,0,,[sign]Kimi wa petto\NYou are my pet
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.07,0:03:27.97,episode,text,0,0,0,,[sign]5. I'll discipline you
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.51,0:03:31.51,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:33.20,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, she's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.20,0:03:34.58,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:39.45,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You must be tired.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.61,0:03:41.58,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh? What?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.28,0:03:45.10,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Aww… Sumire-chan's gotten confused.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.20,0:03:46.70,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I suppose we surprised her, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.75,0:03:49.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm… E-Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.93,0:03:53.76,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hold on a minute. Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.76,0:03:56.25,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,This is my place… and when I called Hasumi-senpai's place, that happened…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:58.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But senpai is here, and Momo is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.07,0:04:00.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Where is the logic in reality that the two are sitting and talking together like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.80,0:04:02.00,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Umm… Iwaya?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.34,0:04:02.97,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:06.98,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,My friend suddenly came over and asked to stay at my place.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.91,0:04:09.01,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Your friend…?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.14,0:04:12.41,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I didn't have a place to sleep, so I left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:17.22,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,And I was wondering if you could let me spend the night at your place tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.79,0:04:20.96,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Is that… so?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.70,0:04:27.73,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.90,0:04:28.70,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.70,0:04:32.93,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I left you a message on your phone, but I seem to have surprised you a great deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.93,0:04:34.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:37.51,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Did you have to work overtime?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.64,0:04:39.71,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, the host server shut down, so I was there until now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.71,0:04:40.84,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Well, I'll be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.84,0:04:41.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.11,0:04:42.98,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I'm going home.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.11,0:04:44.88,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.21,0:04:47.35,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Thank you, Takeshi-kun, for waiting with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:49.78,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,No, it was interesting chatting with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.09,0:04:51.49,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,See you later, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.85,0:04:52.42,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.15,0:04:54.42,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Wait… Mo…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.73,0:05:02.86,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,He said his sister asked him to return a video to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.23,0:05:04.53,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? A video?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.87,0:05:06.20,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,He said he dropped it into your mailbox.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.37,0:05:07.40,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What was it again?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.40,0:05:11.17,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,"Fukawa Ryo's Workshop on How to Overcome Cowardice" or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.04,0:05:15.68,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I thought it was unlikely that you would watch that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.65,0:05:18.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Somewhat…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.98,0:05:23.25,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Well, let's go in.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.25,0:05:28.99,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I was waiting all day for tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.23,0:05:33.86,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, no. I don't really mean it that way…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.40,0:05:38.73,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I mean… it's not that I don't mean it either, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.20,0:05:43.20,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Well… I just thought that we could finally spend some time together without any distractions.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.01,0:05:45.74,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.96,0:06:02.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why is it so messy?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.73,0:06:12.00,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Can I come in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.00,0:06:16.47,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, yes! Come in!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.27,0:06:20.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I made you wait. Please come in.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.34,0:06:21.68,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.61,0:06:26.45,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Hey, where's Momo-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.65,0:06:27.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.88,0:06:34.12,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh… Momo, the dog… Umm… My sister is taking care of Momo right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.12,0:06:36.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Lately I've been sick and have been coming home late, so…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.56,0:06:40.73,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I see, then tonight it's just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.17,0:06:47.90,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,This room's really nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.64,0:06:52.97,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It makes me feel tranquil. It seems like the room of a career woman.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.98,0:06:55.14,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.34,0:06:58.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, would you like something to eat? Or a bath?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.21,0:06:58.85,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.85,0:07:02.05,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.05,0:07:04.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It must be odd to suddenly offer you a bath. It was strange, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.82,0:07:06.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm… I must make something to eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.65,0:07:08.36,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Before I do that, let's turn on the television.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.36,0:07:11.56,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Television… Oh…? Where's the remote control?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:20.80,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You don't have to go through all this trouble for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.04,0:07:24.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.51,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,See, you apologized again.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.91,0:07:34.62,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Right now, I don't need anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.15,0:07:38.42,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,As long as I have you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:55.24,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.84,0:07:58.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}After a month and a half of dating, finally…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.11,0:08:01.81,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Finally I'm able to get her to this stage…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.81,0:08:07.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Although I'm still a little bothered by the whole incident with Fukushima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.92,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}What am I going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.16,0:08:19.49,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Senpai…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.80,0:08:23.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}is really good at kissing.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.50,0:08:25.70,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}What should I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.43,0:08:28.37,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Should I just continue like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.07,0:08:32.01,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,{\i1}Or should I carry her over to the bed?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.05,0:08:45.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.96,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Can we go to your room?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.22,0:08:49.76,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, no. Please put me down.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.80,0:08:51.93,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm heavy. I have more muscle than I appear to.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.03,0:08:53.09,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.28,0:09:17.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Senpai…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.49,0:09:19.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.95,0:09:20.86,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.72,0:09:25.13,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I pulled a muscle.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.26,0:09:27.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.07,0:09:35.44,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you laughing?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.47,0:09:38.91,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,No, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.21,0:09:41.88,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm… I'm really, really sorry about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.98,0:09:44.01,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,You don't have to apologize so much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.31,0:09:46.61,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's not like I came here to have sex.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.08,0:09:49.92,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Well, let's eat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.12,0:09:52.89,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm actually pretty hungry.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:55.06,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Please, go ahead. Although it's nothing much.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.89,0:10:00.36,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.36,0:10:02.36,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.83,0:10:05.63,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Wow, I didn't know you were so good at cooking.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.63,0:10:06.87,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.45,0:10:21.98,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh… Shall I turn on the television?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.35,0:10:26.12,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah, sure. There are so many news bulletins lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.62,0:10:29.42,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh…? The remote…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.53,0:10:32.69,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oops… I threw it up onto the loft…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.36,0:10:35.36,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry. Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.90,0:10:39.13,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, are you okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.13,0:10:40.47,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, the pain has subsided.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.80,0:11:09.20,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Is something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.53,0:11:12.00,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh…? Nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.38,0:11:31.29,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I found it… the remote control.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.29,0:11:32.62,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That's good.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.62,0:11:35.86,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Who could it be at this hour?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.53,0:11:39.53,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's the office.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.63,0:11:44.70,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, Yada? What's up?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.78,0:11:57.85,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,At Jordan?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.95,0:12:00.45,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,That's pretty big news.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.22,0:12:02.45,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What's the current situation?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.45,0:12:06.72,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What about Kimura-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.90,0:12:21.90,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Gotcha… I'll go right away.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.51,0:12:24.51,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Iwaya.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.57,0:12:27.01,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.68,0:12:33.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, I mean… Did something happen in Jordan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.92,0:12:36.55,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,There seems to have been a hijacking situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.09,0:12:41.32,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Kimura-san has gone to Hong Kong, so I'm the only one who can speak directly with them.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.02,0:12:42.66,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.22,0:12:44.63,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.39,0:12:48.36,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then please don't worry about me and go on ahead.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.26,0:12:52.55,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry to do this, especially when you took time off for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:52.60,0:12:54.84,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's fine, don't worry. If it's about your work, it can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.77,0:12:59.54,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Shall I wrap some of this up? Maybe you can eat it at the office?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.48,0:13:03.45,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Iwaya…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.82,0:13:09.75,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:12.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, me too. Sorry that things were so hectic.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.79,0:13:14.76,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.53,0:13:19.69,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'll go now.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.93,0:13:21.73,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Itterasshai.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.08,0:13:38.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That was tiring.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.95,0:13:42.40,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Woohoo!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.40,0:13:43.08,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.08,0:13:46.09,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,It's finally my turn! Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean, "my turn"? Be quiet, it's already 5 in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.80,0:13:53.13,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Because it's my turn to eat! Hurry up and make me something!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.13,0:13:54.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm so tired…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.83,0:13:57.10,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,But it's a pet's right to be fed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.30,0:13:59.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,A normal pet doesn't declare it like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.70,0:14:01.70,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,But I'm starving already!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.70,0:14:05.14,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,When I was about to go buy some dinner, I ran into Hasumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.47,0:14:07.18,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,And…? What did you two talk about anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.08,0:14:10.38,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,A lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.05,0:14:13.52,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,And since when were you over there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.52,0:14:14.18,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,The whole time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.18,0:14:14.72,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.72,0:14:17.12,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,You two were having a long conversation down here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:20.49,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,So I circled around the dumpster and came back in through the back door.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.49,0:14:23.83,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Oh! The video you threw hit my head.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.19,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,How dare you… Why didn't you tell me earlier?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.19,0:14:27.16,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,It was okay for me to speak up?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.16,0:14:28.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, never…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.23,0:14:28.96,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.80,0:14:32.60,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I behaved like a good pet, didn't I? Pat me, pat me!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.67,0:14:37.01,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You wish.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.31,0:14:45.02,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.31,0:14:47.22,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, really…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.75,0:14:51.22,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Oh, good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.22,0:14:52.42,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.43,0:15:01.03,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Morning already…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.01,0:15:15.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,There you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.54,0:15:17.05,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.68,0:15:19.05,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,This is dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.05,0:15:21.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, that's your food. Although it's already time for breakfast.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.65,0:15:24.39,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, what a long night.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.39,0:15:25.69,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Wait, Sumire-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.22,0:15:28.69,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,This is clearly completely different from what you gave Hasumi-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.69,0:15:29.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.79,0:15:31.43,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,This is so much worse than what you gave him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.43,0:15:35.76,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Over there, there was chikuzen-ni, sunny-side-up, burdock and steamed eggs!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.76,0:15:37.40,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,There was even kenchin soup!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.70,0:15:38.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't complain!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.83,0:15:43.77,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because of you, I just had the most stressful time of my life. And I'm awfully exhausted!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.04,0:15:47.74,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I think, even before that, you were already pretty tired…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.92,0:15:59.59,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Didn't you want to ask Hasumi-kun about who stayed at his house last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.82,0:16:00.29,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.92,0:16:05.73,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Apparently some girl from his company was being stalked,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.73,0:16:08.43,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,and she said that if he wouldn't let her stay over, she'd be killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.43,0:16:10.43,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,So he couldn't do anything but let her stay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.87,0:16:13.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,So that's what happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.70,0:16:15.60,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I learned about it while we were waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.60,0:16:18.17,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Aren't I good? So give me a pat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.54,0:16:21.71,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,And if you'd just add in some miso soup, that'd be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.71,0:16:23.61,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,And maybe some pickled side dishes too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.61,0:16:25.25,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Stop being so selfish!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.25,0:16:27.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,If you're a pet, act like one and just be quiet!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.92,0:16:30.42,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Really… I wonder where I went wrong in disciplining you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.30,0:16:42.20,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}At that moment…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.20,0:16:49.50,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}I could faintly smell Fukushima-san's perfume on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.88,0:17:01.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That woman…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.08,0:17:04.05,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What did she do to him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.44,0:17:27.81,Petto_basic,girl,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.71,0:17:31.65,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,See you later, Junpei.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.65,0:17:33.55,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,All right, see you at the studio.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.49,0:17:39.50,Petto_basic,girl,0,0,0,,Good morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.50,0:17:40.96,Petto_basic,girl,0,0,0,,Hey, who was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.96,0:17:42.99,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,My new boyfriend. Isn't he cool?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.19,0:17:45.06,Petto_basic,girl,0,0,0,,You're kidding me! He's so hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.06,0:17:46.56,Petto_basic,girl,0,0,0,,Yeah, he's really good looking!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.43,0:17:54.64,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,You did something to Rumi, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.87,0:17:55.44,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.14,0:17:57.57,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.57,0:17:59.94,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,I'm asking you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.31,0:18:04.68,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,She suddenly grabbed me and asked me to go to a love hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.98,0:18:06.38,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, man…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.45,0:18:09.35,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,She was crying about committing suicide,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.35,0:18:11.29,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,so I let her stay at my house last night and the night before.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:15.22,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Why do I always have to deal with your mistakes?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.39,0:18:17.00,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I wonder why…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.00,0:18:18.29,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,"I wonder why"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.29,0:18:20.66,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,She asked me to kiss her, so I just did what she asked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.76,0:18:22.16,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,I feel like punching you out.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.16,0:18:25.27,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Whenever she sees me, she always goes into a fit of hysteria.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.27,0:18:27.17,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,That's because she likes you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.17,0:18:28.34,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I like her too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.57,0:18:30.47,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.27,0:18:36.78,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,The more we get close to one another, the more it tires us out…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:42.62,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I can't give her any of the things she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.62,0:18:43.72,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,The things she wants?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.75,0:18:47.12,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Then what are you giving that chick whom you live with?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.29,0:18:50.13,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.03,0:18:53.29,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Sorry, Junpei. I'll call you back later.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.43,0:18:59.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I decided to go to work after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.50,0:19:01.20,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Your food is in the refrigerator.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.41,0:19:05.37,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sorry about earlier…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.01,0:19:08.18,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I should be going now.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.55,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,What I'm giving her?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.19,0:19:24.56,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.96,0:19:29.16,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Maybe something like an antidepressant for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.73,0:19:35.84,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,This whole situation is kind of bittersweet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.71,0:19:39.44,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,It's something that happens often.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.14,0:19:48.75,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,In love, there is always a superior and an inferior party.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.98,0:19:50.92,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Superior and inferior?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.50,0:19:52.30,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.46,0:19:55.76,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,It's the "food chain of love".
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.84,0:20:12.14,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.34,0:20:14.91,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh? Iwaya-san, I thought you were taking the day off today.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.68,0:20:18.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,There's nothing to do at home, so I decided to come to work.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.78,0:20:20.49,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,She's a corporate warrior.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.22,0:20:22.72,Petto_basic_2,boss2,0,0,0,,What a sad life for a woman to lead.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.45,0:20:25.02,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Then, can you look over this for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.02,0:20:26.29,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,It's about the next cover article.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.29,0:20:26.69,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:30.96,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,This is really helpful. I've never handled a big article like this before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.96,0:20:32.73,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,I'm lucky to be able to work with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.70,0:20:35.86,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Fukushima-chan, do you have those copies ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.90,0:20:36.60,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.83,0:20:39.60,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Here you go.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.60,0:20:40.14,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.07,0:20:45.07,Petto_basic,Ishida,0,0,0,,Oh, Fukushima-chan, your perfume today is a little too strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.17,0:20:47.64,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Don't say that, Ishidacchi. That's sexual harassment.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.74,0:20:49.88,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,What? Sexual harassment from Ishidacchi again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.41,0:20:52.98,Petto_basic,colleague,0,0,0,,You're too young to be thinking about such things, Ishida!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.98,0:20:55.18,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,Whoa, Iwaya-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.18,0:20:55.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.65,0:20:57.19,Petto_basic,Kuraki,0,0,0,,The bags under your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.02,0:20:59.49,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? Oh…
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.52,0:21:01.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Excuse me for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.46,0:21:08.36,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh my gosh… Wow… They're like stains!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:19.46,0:21:20.44,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.61,0:21:27.05,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Acting all cool and collected again. You dislike me like no other, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.75,0:21:33.62,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,The fact that you like him is not something I can do anything about.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.79,0:21:37.46,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I don't just like him, I want him.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.43,0:21:42.63,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I won't say anything like "break up now", so don't worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.30,0:21:45.30,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,He seems pretty hard to get.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.30,0:21:50.54,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Last night, I tried to seduce him physically, but he just panicked and ran away.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:55.28,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Besides, I decided to spend a little more time on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.61,0:21:58.71,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,After all, my ultimate goal is marriage.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.71,0:22:00.82,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.02,0:22:05.12,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,So you're saying that you don't like Hasumi-senpai, but you just want him?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.12,0:22:06.29,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Perhaps.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.29,0:22:08.12,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Everything's there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.12,0:22:10.39,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,The top education, top income.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.39,0:22:11.63,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Just by things like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.63,0:22:13.43,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Then what about you, Iwaya-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:19.50,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Do you really… like Hasumi-san just for who he is?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.50,0:22:21.40,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Regardless of his educational background, income and looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.34,0:22:28.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Only men who are taller than me, higher in education and income can talk to me like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.88,0:22:32.18,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, of course!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.21,0:22:35.45,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Your birthday's at the end of this month, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:36.35,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.65,0:22:40.49,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,"May 2nd. Lost as to what to get Iwaya for her birthday present.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.39,0:22:44.83,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Honestly speaking, I don't really know what she wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.83,0:22:48.03,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Sometimes she seems to be so self-conscious that I feel bad for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.03,0:22:50.57,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,How can I make her happy?"
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.27,0:22:53.40,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Tada!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.40,0:22:55.07,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hasumi's diary.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:55.67,0:23:00.11,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,One can be so careless when living alone. It didn't even have a lock on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.11,0:23:02.51,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You didn't copy it, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.71,0:23:07.28,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Shall I give it to you? He wrote many other things about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.48,0:23:10.65,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I don't need it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.52,0:23:13.02,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,That's what I thought you'd say.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.16,0:23:17.26,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,And… if you say anything about this to Hasumi-san,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.26,0:23:19.33,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'll spill the beans about your younger boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.50,0:23:23.37,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,The cute boy with the curly hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.10,0:23:26.74,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You look so surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.74,0:23:28.80,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.94,0:23:30.61,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,So it's true?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.81,0:23:34.38,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,You lied to Ishidacchi about having a younger brother, didn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:36.64,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,That kind of stuff, along with your address,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.64,0:23:38.75,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,can be found just by doing a little research at General Affairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:43.59,0:23:49.02,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I haven't told anyone yet. I want to use my last resort wisely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.13,0:23:54.23,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Aren't you ashamed of what you're doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.86,0:23:55.90,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Not at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:01.64,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,When I was 9, my mother left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.64,0:24:05.74,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I always had to take care of my lousy dad and younger brothers. And everything I wanted came last.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:06.34,0:24:09.78,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,After I graduated from high school and came to Tokyo, I didn't have anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:10.95,0:24:13.85,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Unlike you elite people, I didn't have any unnecessary pride either.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.68,0:24:18.89,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,So everything I desire, I'll go through any means to get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.32,0:24:26.19,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I'm just saying that there are some things you can never get just by showing off.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:36.57,0:24:37.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:39.14,0:24:40.68,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.98,0:24:45.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'll make dinner, so come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:03.16,0:25:07.03,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Do you really like…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.03,0:25:08.94,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san just for who he is? Regardless of his educational background, income and looks?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:48.71,0:25:49.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You know what…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:52.18,0:25:54.48,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I really like Hasumi-senpai…
Dialogue: 0,0:25:57.79,0:26:04.76,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Regardless of any conditions… he's really kind, and I can truly respect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.90,0:26:12.57,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But it's painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.51,0:26:27.35,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:32.52,0:26:36.22,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,When I was young, I had a big dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:36.76,0:26:37.53,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:38.33,0:26:38.86,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.86,0:26:46.97,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,To become a ballet dancer with the lightest footstep and most beautiful grace.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.67,0:26:51.81,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,To set foot on stages all around the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:05.32,0:27:06.19,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,However…
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.86,0:27:09.02,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Mama, look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:21.80,0:27:22.77,Petto_basic,girl,0,0,0,,Bravo!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.84,0:27:24.74,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yay!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.48,0:27:35.85,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,However… that dream was obliterated with the appearance of a child prodigy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.99,0:27:38.49,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,What a weak person.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.99,0:27:39.92,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Weak?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:40.82,0:27:41.72,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,On top of that,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.72,0:27:45.03,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,it's a rotten way to find out about the lady who lives in the apartment.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:45.66,0:27:47.53,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,I won't tell you! Never!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.93,0:27:48.76,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.17,0:27:51.27,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,So you can dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.87,0:27:52.43,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.77,0:27:54.57,Petto_basic,landlord,0,0,0,,Can you still dance a little?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.95,0:28:08.92,Petto_basic,nanny,0,0,0,,No. Now all I can do is chase after his back…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.49,0:28:13.49,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,This is him, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.49,0:28:18.49,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's an article that was published when I worked with local news, before I went to Kofu.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.13,0:28:20.20,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,This…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:21.03,0:28:26.43,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,This "Kumakawa Post" won the disfavor of his mother,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.27,0:28:32.71,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,and she called us saying "Please don't taint our Takeshi's image with libel".
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.97,0:28:36.18,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I just happened to answer the phone when she called to yell at us, so that's how I remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.38,0:28:37.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Rozan?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.11,0:28:41.48,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Yeah. It's a worldwide convention for young dancers, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.48,0:28:44.29,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's amazing how such a talented young man is the younger brother of your childhood friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:47.16,0:28:48.76,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I didn't know…
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.22,0:28:53.09,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But he seems to have quit classical dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:53.26,0:28:56.77,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Well, there must be a lot of difficulties in the professional world.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.77,0:29:01.04,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,I got into a fight with my parents and left home.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:02.14,0:29:04.21,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,By the way, thanks for this.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:05.01,0:29:06.88,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You didn't have to wash them.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.11,0:29:12.98,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,My coworkers teased me, saying it was like a loving wife's homemade lunch.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:12.98,0:29:14.28,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? Loving wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.45,0:29:16.69,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It's kind of embarrassing, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.72,0:29:19.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.39,0:29:21.49,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.02,0:29:27.30,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,It wasn't so bad getting a lunchbox and being seen off by you.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.87,0:29:35.27,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}Does this mean…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:38.57,0:29:40.58,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}that if we keep this relationship going…
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.28,0:29:48.95,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}it will eventually lead to marriage?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.55,0:29:51.92,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sorry, I'm late.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:52.15,0:29:53.99,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, I bought you some flan.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.79,0:29:59.09,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Hey, not yet. After dinner.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.70,0:30:03.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,All right, good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:14.74,0:30:16.11,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,There's something wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.08,0:30:24.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, well.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:32.96,0:30:34.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Marriage…?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.14,0:30:41.54,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so? I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.54,0:30:45.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then 10 o'clock, the day after tomorrow, may I meet with you? Thank you, goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.68,0:30:50.68,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I run into you again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:50.68,0:30:52.35,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,It feels like destiny, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.99,0:30:58.72,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,There's a wrinkle between your brows again.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.99,0:31:00.60,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What? A wrinkle?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.60,0:31:01.50,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.42,0:31:05.09,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Reminds me of a sailing youth rather than a Noh-mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:06.46,0:31:08.16,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Is there something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:08.36,0:31:12.40,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No, actually I'm very happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.40,0:31:14.20,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Oh, is that so?
Dialogue: 0,0:31:14.60,0:31:16.20,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is…
Dialogue: 0,0:31:16.44,0:31:21.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,My lover is very sweet, my work is going well, so there should be no discontent.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.61,0:31:25.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yet, something is bothering me… and I can't sleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.02,0:31:30.19,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I think it may be a bone from the mackerel I ate yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.35,0:31:36.39,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Let's talk more later. The next time we meet… as comrades.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:44.10,0:31:45.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:49.07,0:31:50.57,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.94,0:31:57.55,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What is it every day?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:01.12,0:32:03.79,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Something bothers me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:09.82,0:32:11.43,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}This boy…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.73,0:32:17.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}he hasn't uttered a word lately.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.87,0:32:20.74,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Since when? When was it?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.74,0:32:23.64,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,His behavior is as usual, so I didn't notice. But…
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.81,0:32:29.84,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, are you mad about something?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:33.62,0:32:37.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why are you so quiet? Say something.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:46.63,0:32:49.90,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Are you still mad about the breakfast I made you the other day?
Dialogue: 0,0:32:49.90,0:32:52.17,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because I didn't make you any miso soup…
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.88,0:33:02.34,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You're kidding me.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.45,0:33:07.45,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo baby, are you hungry?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:11.00,0:33:12.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh, really?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:15.99,0:33:17.66,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then say "Give me food".
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.13,0:33:23.37,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,"Give me… food". If you don't say it, I won't give you any.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.10,0:33:30.74,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Fine then. I'll eat it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:33.00,0:33:34.24,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:33:38.25,0:33:40.12,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Delicious.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.79,0:33:49.02,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo, your mouth's open.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.87,0:34:01.44,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Say "give me", or else I won't let you have it.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.87,0:34:08.71,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,For the last time, I said I won't give it to you unless you talk!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.25,0:34:21.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Just eat it, then! Don't look at me with those eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:32.73,0:34:35.14,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I lost to my pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.04,0:34:40.14,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,The pet won't talk?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:40.14,0:34:44.41,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Isn't that a given? It would be weirder if it did talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.41,0:34:46.18,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,But Momo's a human.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.18,0:34:49.28,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,But there's no drawback, is there? After all, he's just a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.28,0:34:54.06,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,He's not loud, and he can completely understand what you're saying. It's actually ideal.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:54.06,0:34:55.46,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's true, but…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.46,0:34:57.23,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,You're just keeping him as a pet, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.23,0:34:59.59,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Then it's fine…
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.73,0:35:03.57,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,Unless you want more than that from him.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.80,0:35:06.87,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It's not like that…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.87,0:35:09.07,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Oh! Maybe he's sick.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.07,0:35:11.97,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,How could that energetic kid ever get sick?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.97,0:35:16.08,Petto_basic,Yuri,0,0,0,,If you're going to get that sad about it, get a parrot next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.46,0:35:30.73,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,It couldn't be…
Dialogue: 0,0:35:46.11,0:35:47.18,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:48.41,0:35:49.81,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.07,0:36:16.14,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,After listening to your story, I see no problem with Momo-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.24,0:36:17.74,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I know that.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:17.77,0:36:20.94,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,He's a very well-disciplined good dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.28,0:36:25.08,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,He can go to the bathroom on his own, and he can even dance.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.08,0:36:27.42,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I know that very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.78,0:36:31.82,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,So I wasn't really asking for advice about the pet…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.82,0:36:34.26,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I was just making conversation.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.26,0:36:38.19,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you not to get too emotionally involved with your pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.19,0:36:39.59,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,You did?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.59,0:36:43.33,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Well, I should speak for myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.33,0:36:44.90,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Right, Rudolph?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.07,0:36:48.67,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Umm… Doctor, how are we comrades?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:48.97,0:36:51.04,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,In the sense that we both can't love people.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:51.44,0:36:53.04,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,That's not true…
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.31,0:37:02.18,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I have a boyfriend and the relationship is going very well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:02.18,0:37:05.79,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Then why don't you go talk to your boyfriend about
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.79,0:37:09.42,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,these troubles and uncertainties that you're carrying right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.23,0:37:12.89,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,He must be a fine, dependable man.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:13.63,0:37:15.16,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.16,0:37:17.10,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Ah… You can't act spoiled in front of him?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.10,0:37:20.77,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Of course not…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.47,0:37:25.24,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I'm going to ask you some questions, so I want you to answer truthfully.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:25.44,0:37:31.88,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Are you telling this boyfriend how much you love him everyday?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:32.70,0:37:33.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.78,0:37:36.02,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,And the reason you can't is…?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:38.69,0:37:40.00,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.00,0:37:41.36,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Why is it embarrassing?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.76,0:37:43.46,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because I get shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:43.46,0:37:44.76,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Why do you become shy?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.13,0:37:46.83,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What do you mean why…
Dialogue: 0,0:37:46.83,0:37:50.38,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Then I'll change the questions. You own a pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:50.40,0:37:51.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.20,0:37:53.10,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Can you tell Momo-chan that you love him?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.10,0:37:53.97,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Yes, I can.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.97,0:37:55.74,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Can you hug him on your own initiative?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.14,0:37:56.50,Petto_basic_2,Sumire,0,0,0,,I can!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.74,0:37:56.93,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Why is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.93,0:37:58.77,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Because I love him, and he's adorable.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:58.77,0:38:00.78,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Why don't you become shy with him?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.68,0:38:05.48,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why? He's not the kind that I would get shy around.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:05.61,0:38:07.55,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,You act spoiled around your pet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.16,0:38:16.19,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,The pet's the one that's being spoiled.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.19,0:38:23.06,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,There is a relationship of ownership between animals and humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.90,0:38:31.37,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,To put it simply, humans will betray other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.37,0:38:35.48,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,But, a pet will never betray its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.74,0:38:42.12,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,If we know that they will not betray us, we can tell them 100% openly how much we love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.59,0:38:50.33,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I will probably only be able to live with pets the rest of my life.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.73,0:38:53.26,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,With pets the rest of your life?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.26,0:39:00.17,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I sometimes wish that I was born a simpler animal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:05.61,0:39:08.34,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Today's appointment is free of charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:08.71,0:39:11.55,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I talked too much about unnecessary matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.99,0:39:21.10,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Humans will betray other humans.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.20,0:39:25.46,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,But, a pet will never betray its owner.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.46,0:39:29.10,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Then what if the pet is a human?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.27,0:39:31.70,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.84,0:39:41.58,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Well, you've got to have them check on that.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.24,0:39:45.01,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.01,0:39:46.21,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:48.55,0:39:50.69,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Why are you talking, Momo?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.25,0:39:54.12,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,Hello? Takeshi?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:55.29,0:39:57.23,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,Oh, sorry… Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:58.33,0:40:02.30,Petto_basic,Takeshi,0,0,0,,I better go now. I'll talk to you later. Bye.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:22.35,0:40:26.12,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Isn't it obvious? Did you actually think that I was a dog?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.43,0:40:32.19,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome home!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.16,0:40:37.57,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Say it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:38.07,0:40:39.53,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome home.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.83,0:40:41.17,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,One more time.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.10,0:40:45.74,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome back, Sumire-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.28,0:40:52.61,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}This is what was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.06,0:41:06.86,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,{\i1}These words that were always my comforting salvation.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.47,0:41:15.00,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm home.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.51,0:41:25.58,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I'm back, Momo.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:29.22,0:41:30.49,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Welcome back.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.86,0:41:43.77,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Don't test me.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.63,0:41:48.24,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I need you enough already.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:53.78,0:41:56.01,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Stay a good boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:00.22,0:42:01.65,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:11.83,0:42:15.53,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}This may be too much, coming from a pet,
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.70,0:42:26.31,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}but I wish she'd see a little more… just a little more of the value of my existence.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.02,0:42:39.82,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:39.82,0:42:43.63,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, can I sleep with you tonight?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:45.26,0:42:46.03,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.93,0:42:47.70,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,Come on.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:49.00,0:42:49.76,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:50.93,0:42:54.40,Petto_basic_ending,Sumire,0,0,0,,But if you do anything weird, I'll kill you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:56.00,0:42:57.00,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.84,0:43:02.94,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}I want her to feel strongly that she needs me
Dialogue: 0,0:43:04.41,0:43:08.72,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}and not taking for granted that we're always together.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:10.59,0:43:12.29,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}More than anyone…
Dialogue: 0,0:43:14.82,0:43:16.06,Petto_basic_ending,Momo,0,0,0,,{\i1}Always.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:19.03,0:43:20.03,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:21.16,0:43:22.80,Petto_basic_ending,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:27.37,0:43:29.50,Petto_basic_ending,nice_girl,0,0,0,,You didn't go home last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.77,0:43:40.82,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,You probably already know, but I failed in a marriage once when I was young.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:40.82,0:43:42.92,Petto_basic_ending,nice_girl,0,0,0,,I didn't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.72,0:43:48.49,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,I loved her. But I couldn't tell her that.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:50.13,0:43:57.40,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,It's not that I disliked her, but it was embarrassing and difficult to say those words.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.40,0:44:00.67,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,Becoming inferior… inferior.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:06.88,0:44:09.68,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,I was afraid of becoming the inferior one.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.25,0:44:19.75,Petto_basic_ending,counsel,0,0,0,,There were many problems within the marriage, but I think this was the most direct problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:21.06,0:44:24.63,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I cannot love a woman with all my body and soul…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.63,0:44:26.63,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,because I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:30.70,0:44:32.10,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I'm afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:32.63,0:44:33.87,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Afraid?
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.94,0:44:38.91,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,Yes, afraid… very afraid.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:39.87,0:44:41.48,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,But…
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.04,0:44:44.71,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I cannot live alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:50.42,0:44:51.99,Petto_basic,nice_girl,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.12,0:44:53.66,Petto_basic,counsel,0,0,0,,I love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:56.16,0:44:59.03,Petto_basic,Junpei,0,0,0,,I like you… a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.23,0:45:00.26,Petto_basic,Rumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:06.37,0:45:08.00,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,Oh, Fukushima-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:08.90,0:45:12.41,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,I like you, Hasumi-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.04,0:45:19.48,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, but this makes things difficult for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:20.08,0:45:23.92,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,I'm seeing Iwaya with the hopes of marrying her someday.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.92,0:45:26.79,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,It's fine. I don't mind at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:26.99,0:45:27.96,Petto_basic,Hasumi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.76,0:45:33.06,Petto_basic,Fukushima,0,0,0,,Hasumi-san, you will soon come to like me.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.27,0:45:42.64,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,I feel so happy on mornings when I have no work.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:44.54,0:45:50.28,Petto_basic,Momo,0,0,0,,Hey, even if you get married… will you still own me as a pet?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.15,0:45:53.15,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,Silly…
Dialogue: 0,0:45:53.48,0:45:55.68,Petto_basic,Sumire,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?